sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User
  participant GW as Gateway API
  participant ORCH as Orchestrator
  participant POL as Policy Engine
  participant SLM as SLM Service

  User->>GW: Request
  GW->>ORCH: Forward request
  ORCH->>POL: Evaluate policy
  POL-->>ORCH: allow
  ORCH->>SLM: /v1/infer/sync
  SLM-->>ORCH: completion
  ORCH-->>GW: result
  GW-->>User: 200 OK
